title: (Wed Early Bird) Bobby and Caitlin’s Relationship Songs + Lunchbox’s Close Call Biking from Work + Amy’s Question of the Day: Can You share a loofah with a Significant Other?
itunes:title: (Wed Early Bird) Bobby and Caitlin’s Relationship Songs + Lunchbox’s Close Call Biking from Work + Amy’s Question of the Day: Can You share a loofah with a Significant Other?
description:
Bobby shares the songs that define each chapter of his and his wife Caitlin’s relationship. Lunchbox had the first time where he questioned biking to work. We also found out how much money he’s saved on gas doing this. Amy brings in her question of the day if we think it’s okay to share a loofah with a significant other? She finds it gross!
